### TOP1 Salomon Speedcross 6 GTX (High-End All-Terrain Type)
- **Core Anti-Slip Logic**:
  1. The sole uses **Contagrip MA exclusive mud rubber**, which has strong adhesion and durability, allowing it to break through wet and slippery water films directly bite the road surface;
  2. The iconic "8mm deep wolf tooth pattern" + "multi-directional interlaced grooves": Deep teeth grip terrain, while interlaced grooves quickly drain mud or积水to avoid the grooves being blocked by mud losing traction;  
  3. A wide tread design enhances side slip stability, suitable for muddy slopes in southern mountainous areas.
- **Applicable Scenarios**: Complex mountain all-terrain hiking, jungle trekking.

