- **Core Anti-Slip Logic**:
  1. The sole is equipped with **Vibram Megagrip premium wet rubber**, which achieves a static friction coefficient of 0.8 on water-stained stones and muddy grasslands (ordinary rubber only achieves 0.4-0.6);
  2. A "radial deep grooves + segmented drainage holes": Radial grooves guide积水to flow out quickly, while segmented holes prevent soft mud from embedding;  
  3. The midsole Dynamic Suspension System (DSS) provides cushioning and locks the ankle to avoid side flips in muddy ground.
- **Applicable Scenarios**: Long-distance heavy load hiking, high-altitude rainy season crossing.

