### TOP10 Columbia Newton Ridge Plus II Mid GTX (Classic All-Terrain Type)
- **Core Anti-Slip Logic**:
  1. Uses **Omni-Grip all-terrain anti-slip rubber**, optimized for southern wet stone/soft grass mud;
